+  (thanks to Tobias Grimm). Unknown symbols are replaced with a '?'.
+- Updated the Slovenian OSD texts (thanks to Matjaz Thaler).
+- Updated the Czech OSD texts (thanks to Vladimír Bárta and Jiri Dobry).
